headline.main: Brandon Marshall Is Expected to Join Growing List of Jets’ Castoffs
headline.print_headline: Marshall Is Expected to Join Growing List of Jets’ Castoffs

lead_paragraph: The Jets are continuing their off-season roster purge by releasing Marshall, a wide receiver who was set to make $7.5 million this season.
